Class WrappedSslContextSPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.net.ssl.SSLContextSpi
      • akka.http.impl.engine.http2.WrappedSslContextSPI

  • public class WrappedSslContextSPI
extends javax.net.ssl.SSLContextSpi
    INTERNAL API

    Wraps an SSLContext so that all engines it creates will announce HTTP/2 if possible.
